cf.60aed61fa61b74674667c2770e986bad.png 1024w, /assets/static/website_browser.2665e34.60aed61fa61b74674667c2770e986bad.png 1920w, /assets/static/website_browser.42db587.60aed61fa61b74674667c2770e986bad.png 2560w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/website_browser.42db587.60aed61fa61b74674667c2770e986bad.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/website_browser.42db587.60aed61fa61b74674667c2770e986bad.png\" width=\"2560\"></noscript>\n<br/></p>\n<p><em>Note: In the <a href=\"https://marketplace.threefold.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ThreeFold Now Marketplace</a>, you will see separate widgets for Website, Blog, &#x26; Wiki.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>You can access Website Publisher on the ThreeFold Now Marketplace directly <a href=\"https://marketplace.threefold.io/marketplace/#/solutions/website\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</em></li>\n<li><em>You can access Blog Publisher on the ThreeFold Now Marketplace directly <a href=\"https://marketplace.threefold.io/marketplace/#/solutions/blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</em></li>\n<li><em>You can access Wiki Publisher on the ThreeFold Now Marketplace directly <a href=\"https://marketplace.threefold.io/marketplace/#/solutions/wiki\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</em></li>\n<li><em>Please note that the marketplace is currently running on testnet.</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p>For website (or blog or wiki) creation and management, there are may options available in the market. From total end-to-end solutions like Squarespace to do-it-yourself (and select the tools and software to run your website). ThreeFold has created publishing tools that allow for deployment and management with version control, automatic update, and staging facilities.</p>\n<h2 id=\"why-use-these-solutions\"><a href=\"#why-use-these-solutions\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Why use these solutions?</h2>\n<p>While the tools available in the market tend to make things quite easy, they come with disadvantaged.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Primarily, they run your website on centralized cloud solutions, which brings strong issues around privacy and security.</li>\n<li>\n<p>In addition, website builders generate closed source websites</p>\n<ul>\n<li>This means you cannot access and export your work from these platforms easily</li>\n<li>And you are stuck with the feature sets of these platforms until they decide to expand</li>\n<li>Open source gives full control to website creators and full flexibility</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note that building and deploying a website using these tools does require more technical know-how and obviously the ease of use of website builders is a huge draw. So, in the short term this is not for everybody, but we'll be optimizing this for the everyday person as we go.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 2560 1632' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-e19d442be6c8a378a108e5144a3d9f07'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-e19d442be6c8a378a108e5144a3d9f07)' width='2560' height='1632' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAApCAYAAACFki9MAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAALWklEQVRo3uVaW2yVWRWGokaDjcjtcSKRhIEOJCQOEZU7Rc/Qiw9yiZEnX5wXEx80TmKwJsYHfWAyYZ4MozgYH4wkDkxpS9vT0xZaKAyFpmWA9vScnvv9/Oc/9/5nL9da%2b9/n/OecthSKTtW/%2bbL3vy/r3/vba6299j5dc%2bLEiTX/b8%2bxY8eqC5qbm7d%2bv63V1t7eYmttb7N9t/mY7ee/e9/2wZDb9ieH03ZlxGv7252A7fKw23bJPmO7NICwT9v%2bPDxnu/D3IdvJky2Ik7aWlhYG5a3vS6G1tXVJKHnWPtZ32abStq49ju2tFsb32lpbsahlN835%2bPHjayORiCTgO/u/9bOfvtUMP/7Rfvj2Dw/Dvm/sgz9e%2bgDS%2bXmY8wZg2umGWbcXND0LxRJAY